<p>John and Dave kick off July with this awesome Premium episode. Topics covered include WYSIWYG font menus, controlling Safari&rsquo;s PDF plugin, various backup questions (including one about backing up across the Internet to a friend&rsquo;s house), and much, much more. Subscribe today for just US$25 and enjoy an additional two episodes per month from your two favorite geeks!</p>
